{"tid":1702312,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"求upgrade 意見","createTime":"2019-11-09T15:24:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T15:48:01.000Z","uid":134806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7cc86597ab8aed54ea130bbd0471b75e1b8c764e","tid":1702312,"uid":134806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:24:02.000Z","msg":"小弟新手，部機之前係高登搵list 拎去中央田切番黎，而家部機有時出現情況不斷重新開機<br />\n而家剩係想到換個ssd，但budget 有限得$ 2000，可以點upgrade?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j1WUgKg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj1WUgKg.png&h=58fe344a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e388131896dc8dc5f3d17b4dc9f72296ebdb873","tid":1702312,"uid":180854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cc86597ab8aed54ea130bbd0471b75e1b8c764e","tid":1702312,"uid":134806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:24:02.000Z","msg":"小弟新手，部機之前係高登搵list 拎去中央田切番黎，而家部機有時出現情況不斷重新開機<br />\n而家剩係想到換個ssd，但budget 有限得$ 2000，可以點upgrade?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j1WUgKg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj1WUgKg.png&h=58fe344a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:32:45.000Z","msg":"第一<br />\n部機重新開機可以好多原因<br />\n可以係U, 可以係牛, 可以係底板, 可以係RAM<br />\n不過正常就唔關SSD/HDD事<br />\n所以你換SSD只係會快左, 但係應該都會重新開機, 解決唔到你而家既問題<br />\n第二<br />\n上面講左唔關SSD/HDD事<br />\n而如果要換U/板/RAM, 因為你部機既件已經係幾代之前既事<br />\n所以你預要成套換, 無返三千都唔駛落樓<br />\n<br />\n所以你得兩千銀既話, 又無FD識電腦野<br />\n你都係拎上A-SHOP比人CHECK下咩事, 再睇下有無得搞好過"},{"pid":"1a69831724525b1600050f4ec9df8e99720f7b8a","tid":1702312,"uid":28668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:43:50.000Z","msg":"換隻火牛試一排先 往後十年都用得返"},{"pid":"fb34c6260e7576fe2b09c6b9abc7f616666a5943","tid":1702312,"uid":28668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a69831724525b1600050f4ec9df8e99720f7b8a","tid":1702312,"uid":28668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:43:50.000Z","msg":"換隻火牛試